# This example commits every build artifact (.claude-plugin/*.json,
# CLAUDE.md, agents/*.md, skills/*/SKILL.md, commands/*.md) so a reader
# can inspect the full pipeline output without running `textus build`.
# In a real plugin you'd likely ignore the consumer-side mirrors instead.

# Local runtime artifacts — not source.
/.textus/audit.log
/.textus/notify.log
/.textus/last-build.log
/.textus/.last-build.json
